  <h2>
    <span>喜欢读&#34;绝代双骄（全三册）&#34;的人也喜欢的电子书</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


    <div class="tips-mod">
        支持 Web、iPhone、iPad、Android 阅读器
    </div>
    <div class="content clearfix">
        
        <dl>
            <dt>
            <a href="https://read.douban.com/ebook/107156/?dcs=subject-rec&amp;dcm=douban&amp;dct=1089517" target="_blank">
                <span class="cover-outer">
                <img src="https://pic.arkread.com/cover/ebook/f/107156.1653713934.jpg!cover_default.jpg">
                </span>
            </a>
            </dt>
